Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:23.14,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}朝向月亮奏响的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:30.38,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}我定下心寻找着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:37.24,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}我就在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:50.77,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}幼年时的记忆呼唤着我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:58.37,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}我想踏上寻觅的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:04.12,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}但却得不到机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:08.38,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}不过你依然会保护我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.38,0:21:11.41,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}看到你伸出的援手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:18.06,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}还有那对坚定的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:26.42,Song-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur5\fax-0.15}我想要轻轻放下
